CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 6, 1952, page 13, reads: "All Parts of County - Workers from many districts attended. Among them were: Dewey Foulkes, Sarah Martin, Mr. Mrs. William Finch, Mr. and Mrs. Nathaniel Adams, A. Marguerita Hall, and George W. Childress. Needless to say they enjoyed themselves immensely."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait including Dewey Foulkes, Sarah Martin, Mr. and Mrs. William Finch, Mr. and Mrs. Nathaniel Adams, A. Marguerita Hall, and George W. Childress, seated at banquet table in Syria Mosque for the county Republican victory celebration
